references: Repealing: Ord 42589, Ord 45685, Ord 46748, Ord 48199, Ord 49184, Ord 49523, Ord 57409, Ord 59171, Ord 59175
summary: An ordinance relating to and regulating the conveyance of passengers and baggage for hire in the City of Seattle, fixing the rates therefor, providing penalties for violation thereof, and repealing ordinances numbered 42589, 45685, 46748, 48199, 49184, 49523, 57409, 59171, 59175 and all other ordinances and parts of ordinances in conflict herewith.
